file.name: cm.yaml
file.content:
components:
  schemas:
    tmp0:
      properties:
        id: {type: string}
        successful: {type: string}
      type: object
  securitySchemes:
    BasicAuth: {scheme: basic, type: http}
info:
  contact: {email: frikky@shuffler.io, name: '@frikkylikeme', url: 'https://twitter.com/frikkylikeme'}
  description: Automated generation of Fireeye Cm
  title: Fireeye Cm
  version: 1.0.0
  x-logo: data:image/png;base64,
openapi: 3.0.2
paths:
  tmp0:
    post:
      description: Submit a URL to FireEye CM
      parameters:
      - description: URL to submit
        example: http://asdfasdf.net/bad.php
        in: query
        name: URL
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Profile to use for analysis
        example: win7-sp1
        in: query
        name: Profile
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: ID of an analysis application to use, defaults to -1 to let the
          system decide
        example: '2'
        in: body
        name: Analysis Application ID
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: How long to wait in seconds before giving up on the analysis,
          defaults to 200
        example: '250'
        in: body
        name: Timeout
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp0'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: FireEye CM Submit URL
tags:
- {name: Network Security & Management}
